race.comment: DAD'S PLUM SAUCE (8) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing seventh (25.81) last time in a Mix 6/7 at this track. Can make amends. JOSIE'S SHADOW (7) was out of the placings last time but recorded an impressive Maiden win (26.02) at this track three runs back. Well placed here and should do much better. NOVA'S FERN (3) stalked lead from an outside box last start before finishing third (27.82) at Horsham in a Mix 6/7 over 485m. Well placed and gets her chance. PAGODA GROWLER (4) is new here but can play a major role.
